tedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T12:04:47.000Z","msg":"收下巴"},{"pid":"eed1d14f1859622315bc821348d8e5c890ce0099","tid":2269194,"uid":266131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"519c111163d36809fea461a0a2efad82fb33bbc9","tid":2269194,"uid":266131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T09:31:48.000Z","msg":"咩叫lock頸"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T12:40:40.000Z","msg":"我成日都有做，但冇乜用咁<br />\n<br />\n然後物理治療師話唔做可能重差<br />\n<br />\n我骨科醫生就話我日常姿勢咁差，做得個少少都冇用，但慣左好難改<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3688f8ebc6444d2d18ee3899933ad87eeda90c0","tid":2269194,"uid":216162,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"eed1d14f1859622315bc821348d8e5c890ce0099","tid":2269194,"uid":266131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"519c111163d36809fea461a0a2efad82fb33bbc9","tid":2269194,"uid":266131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T09:31:48.000Z","msg":"咩叫lock頸"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T12:40:40.000Z","msg":"我成日都有做，但冇乜用咁<br />\n<br />\n然後物理治療師話唔做可能重差<br />\n<br />\n我骨科醫生就話我日常姿勢咁差，做得個少少都冇用，但慣左好難改<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T12:44:25.000Z","msg":"做gym同拉筋啦 練返啲背肌改善返好日常姿勢 身體就會自然調整"},{"pid":"df036423996e958cb6a0b5852b4357b3024b6baf","tid":2269194,"uid":30274,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T12:48:04.000Z","msg":"老老實實<br />\n外國好多教健體嘅YouTuber都有講改善嘅exercise，我自己覺得極有用<br />\n但前題係一定要堅持做一段時間，每日，連續兩個月以上<br />\n好過你出去啲濕鳩脊醫，又貴又冇用，一定叫你買package, 每次舒緩你30分鐘之後打回原形<br />\n<br />\n另外極重要係搵到個啱嘅枕頭support頸椎。唔一定貴嘅好但真係靠自己試，可能最後買到一屋枕頭都冇個啱都唔奇，但冇辦法只有試"},{"pid":"03cead824acd1e46024e3df01c7ddc7c8ed2c429","tid":2269194,"uid":56280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d6e062bc5dba3f207b7501acfc2784bac2552e17","tid":2269194,"uid":51566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d9f670478fd0400e077d1072be90544f29efd35f","tid":2269194,"uid":56280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T09:36:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T11:37:23.000Z","msg":"個脊醫有冇叫你做頸部牽引 要收幾錢？？？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T13:30:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21e95d2e906b05a54fd570654511ad8640c6285e","tid":2269194,"uid":292493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6d09253d51faf27e0c152af7cc28c7e906a2e238","tid":2269194,"uid":51566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"298c440569c98f98132d95c297005fdf8c8961a6","tid":2269194,"uid":51566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3977b9124742caa4ffa0f7ec1042c5a8a2ae2e9e","tid":2269194,"uid":63154,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-04T09:18:31.000Z","msg":"我都有頸直但已經好咗好多，知道咗問題根源係寒背，於是我經常練引體上升，同inverted row，肩胛骨冇再僵硬，轉動幅度大返，膊頭容易壓返低，胸部容易挺返起，條頸最後會自我修正，當你啲恒心放錯咗地方，做幾耐都冇用"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T09:26:50.000Z","msg":"姐係要練返你果d 動作會改到？"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T11:34:49.000Z","msg":"大既練左幾耐先好返一半？<br />\n<br />\n最近呢幾日仲嚴重左 <br />\n隻手開始麻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T23:44:37.000Z","msg":"我建議你keep住睇物理治療 <br />\n你呢種情況係壓到cervical nerve 導致手部有numbness<br />\n如果你係做完運動先覺得嚴重左 咁好大可能你做錯左個運動 建議問返你個physio 或者個運動本身唔岩你做 你睇physio佢應該會幫你睇下個form etc 唔好上網自學果d exercises啦 🙏 你呢個case 應該要有physio去follow up<br />\n睇物理治療佢除左幫你做treatment 仲會比d運動你係屋企做 希望你到時會有改善 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6aa2d86cbeb318d3c7d0d92e03b392671e4f97e","tid":2269194,"uid":105602,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T23:53:54.000Z","msg":"我都有，會好易訓矮頸，兩三個月一次，每次頸郁唔到，睇過醫生做加換左個有孤度既枕頭。以家未試過痛返，個枕頭好重要，要用個枕頭會頂起條頸但係頭向後"},{"pid":"5dfb517e05df222ed1e870e40a77c571548c6e8a","tid":2269194,"uid":51566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"df036423996e958cb6a0b5852b4357b3024b6baf","tid":2269194,"uid":30274,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T12:48:04.000Z","msg":"老老實實<br />\n外國好多教健體嘅YouTuber都有講改善嘅exercise，我自己覺得極有用<br />\n但前題係一定要堅持做一段時間，每日，連續兩個月以上<br />\n好過你出去啲濕鳩脊醫，又貴又冇用，一定叫你買package, 每次舒緩你30分鐘之後打回原形<br />\n<br />\n另外極重要係搵到個啱嘅枕頭support頸椎。唔一定貴嘅好但真係靠自己試，可能最後買到一屋枕頭都冇個啱都唔奇，但冇辦法只有試"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T02:42:05.000Z","msg":"有咩邊D 枕頭牌子比教岩直頸症既人用?<br />\n呢幾年用開果D U 枕, 唔覺有咩大分別"},{"pid":"63fd389a4a4c9b65b0009f7d37f506cfb7b733c9","tid":2269194,"uid":51566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"03cead824acd1e46024e3df01c7ddc7c8ed2c429","tid":2269194,"uid":56280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d6e062bc5dba3f207b7501acfc2784bac2552e17","tid":2269194,"uid":51566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d9f670478fd0400e077d1072be90544f29efd35f","tid":2269194,"uid":56280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T09:36:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T11:37:23.000Z","msg":"個脊醫有冇叫你做頸部牽引 要收幾錢？？？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T13:30:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T02:43:13.000Z","msg":"你做左多年次,覺得WORK 唔WORK<br />\n如果有錢可以買返健康, 實會去做, <br />\n但最驚做完無乜效果"},{"pid":"b32dd1da3df3ad46b24b46f1860701790bf6bb0f","tid":2269194,"uid":51566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"21e95d2e906b05a54fd570654511ad8640c6285e","tid":2269194,"uid":292493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6d09253d51faf27e0c152af7cc28c7e906a2e238","tid":2269194,"uid":51566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"298c440569c98f98132d95c297005fdf8c8961a6","tid":2269194,"uid":51566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"reply